WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.965
I love the way that this is real. This is a

00:00:03.965 --> 00:00:09.678
very inspired choice. What I would do is instead of showing

00:00:09.678 --> 00:00:15.275
the toggles, which I would maybe even remove, I would just

00:00:15.275 --> 00:00:19.939
start with the waveform and just be like, “See it in

00:00:19.939 --> 00:00:25.070
action,” instead of “What it might sound like.” And then I

00:00:25.070 --> 00:00:30.434
think what we could do is have our overlay animations as

00:00:30.434 --> 00:00:30.900
well.
